items.title: Firmware update
items.message:
<script>alert(‘XSS’)</script>Firmware update successful

Note: The server firmware is already up to date with specified baseline 2021.03.32.0(31 Mar 2021). The specified baseline has been set for the server.

items.title: Firmware update failed
items.recommendedAction: Please retry the update. If it still fails, log in to the ilo console, collect log files, and then contact HPE Cloud Console support.
